{"tid":44210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拉麵達人沾麵聖者劍心稱要皇天擊殺對他落井下石嘅PK!!!","createTime":"2016-12-18T05:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T10:39:45.000Z","uid":38665,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c45c1f97e355a19465c5c7000c23c1eda798f5","tid":44210,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"[太公報專訊](記者鄭活祖) <br />\n有香港之恥、潮流教主、沾麵聖者、拉麵達人、落車始祖、人生教練、旅遊皇者、星級司儀、禦寒聖手、櫻花神算、丼飯食家、愛情教祖、日影專家、和食尊者等稱號的香港首屈一指人氣博客兼香江第二才子劍心經歷了上月對他的網絡攻擊，深深感受到網絡黑社會的威力，更對向他落井下石的人感到憤怒。餘怒未消的他日前在面書上再向那些網絡黑社會宣戰，說對他落井下石的都是PK陷家剷，並向對他雪中送炭的朋友表示感謝。<br />\n記者就此事向劍心查詢，劍心稱：「那些網絡黑社會只是一堆虛耗光陰的廢柴，在下不會再回應他們的無理攻擊，他們惡貫滿盈，遲早會被皇天擊殺！在下並在此向讀者們承諾，定必迎難而上，為各讀者帶來有用的資訊！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/135601_33b577acb3a75ab734113991aff425c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F135601_33b577acb3a75ab734113991aff425c0.jpg&h=c86dd679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/18/135634_10bd79ab3965c073a7a7ae36daf9fd95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F18%2F135634_10bd79ab3965c073a7a7ae36daf9fd95.jpg&h=80722214&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53c9e119fdce4ef9062aa5cb3641ae59bff2a964","tid":44210,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:01:48.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n拉麵達人沾麵聖者劍心化身壽司專家品評米芝蓮三星名店<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum14.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5850293&amp;highlight_id=217276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum14.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5850293%26highlight_id%3D217276&d=BpxmFN32749DdikvfqNz2ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=1bef03a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum14.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5850293&amp;highlight_id=217276</a><br />\n拉麵達人沾麵聖者劍心成功爭取見報！<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5814727\" data-sr-